True Crime Tues\day presents: The Invisible Death Strike of Havana Syndrome with Franc Milburn!

Across the Globe, American diplomats, Government workers, Top Secret Agents, and Aerospace Scientists have reported symptoms of and even died from conditions of something called Havana Syndrome. A combination of microwave, RF, and other radiation burns that are secretly transmitted to a person secretly to cause traumatic and horrific injury!

Former British Military intelligence officer and paratrooper, Franc Milburn joins True Crime Tuesday to talk about how Havana Syndrome is being used right now by Russia and China against the Aerospace industry and other American agencies, and also delves into the subjects of UAP and Disclosure!
